[[SECTION]]
TITLE: Software source code and supporting documentation

[TEXT]
STATEMENT: >>>
This section constitutes the Software Source Code and supporting documentation
as required by EN 50716:2023, Clause 7.5 and Table A.1 (document 18). It
records the source code baseline, coding standard compliance evidence, static
analysis results, and build configuration for the implemented software components.
<<<

