    Purpose, parameters (name, type, direction, range), return values,
    preconditions, postconditions, and SIL classification.
    As specified in CD-042.

Compliance of source code annotations shall be verified by the static
analysis tool configuration (CI-030) and confirmed during code review (CI-090).
