[ACTION_ITEM]
UID: PR-CI-001
STATUS: Closed
TITLE: <COMP-01>: boundary check missing for <param_2> when <param_1> = 0
STATEMENT: >>>
Defect found during test CTR-004 (interface test, precondition violation).
When <param_1> = 0, the range check for <param_2> was skipped due to an
early-exit condition that bypassed the validation block.
Impact: ERR_RANGE not returned for an invalid <param_2> value in this case;
output was indeterminate. Potential safety impact: <assess>.
Fix applied: added validation of <param_2> before the early exit.
Re-test: CTR-004 re-executed after fix; PASS.
<<<
OWNER: <Developer Name>
DUE_DATE: <YYYY-MM-DD>
COMMENT: >>>
Resolved in source revision <hash>. Re-test evidence in CTR-004 ACTUAL_RESULT.
Static analysis rule added to detect similar patterns.
<<<

